'''7.5 cm Pak 41'''是[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]後期進入服役，由德國製造的[[反坦克炮|反坦克炮]]。它也是錐膛炮（由德國工程師 Hermann Gerlich 在1920年代所提出，可提供更高的砲口初速進而提高穿透力，常用於獵槍上）中口徑最大的。<ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=7OEDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA208&dq=Popular+Science+1933+plane+%22Popular+Mechanics%22&hl=en&ei=v_wHTomlB6H30gG6tLzMCw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=6&sqi=2&ved=0CD4Q6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q&f=true "Mile-A-Second Rifle Bullet Is Squeezed In Firing"] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=7OEDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA208&dq=Popular+Science+1933+plane+%22Popular+Mechanics%22&hl=en&ei=v_wHTomlB6H30gG6tLzMCw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=6&sqi=2&ved=0CD4Q6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q&f=true |date=20140610163646 }} ''Popular Mechanics'', August 1933</ref>

它很像同是縮徑砲的Waffe 0725但口徑不同。<ref name="waffe">{{cite web|url= http://forum.axishistory.com/viewtopic.php?t=23571|title= Question about the waffe 0725|last1= 'daveh'|date= 2 June 2003|website= Axis History Forum|access-date= 25 Oct 2015|quote= "Given the standards of research of T Jentz ... It would appear that the waffe 0725 is a different weapon to the Pak 41."|archive-date= 2016-03-05|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160305010402/http://forum.axishistory.com/viewtopic.php?t=23571|dead-url= no}}</ref>

==研發與設計==
由[[蒂森克虏伯|蒂森克虏伯]]所設計的Pak 41打算利用錐膛炮的設計來增加炮口初速以和[[萊茵金屬|萊茵金屬]]的[[Pak_40反坦克炮|Pak 40]]競爭。除了使用[[鎢|鎢]]芯彈的錐膛炮設計外，Pak 41還有一些特點。其一是將炮管分為三段，靠炮閂側口徑一致且有[[膛線|膛線]]，中間段口徑逐漸縮小且為滑膛，靠炮口端最後70cm口徑恢復一致但沒有刻劃膛線。

